title: Jermaine Wiggins with Birk and PA #92Noon!
description: Jermaine Wiggins was part of Tom Brady's first Super Bowl victory following the 2001 season. He was then a Vikings TE and teammate of Matt Birk's. He chats with Birk and PA!
